Installing
==========
Works on linux only by now.

Running the console demo.
  git clone https://code.google.com/p/mepinta/
  cd mepinta/mepinta
  deploy.py ../../mepinta_deployment
  cd ../../mepinta_deployment
  mepinta_demo.py     #lists the demos
  mepinta_demo.py 0   #run the first one
  mepinta_tests.py    #run all the tests (no too much right now)

For running the some of the Python demos you need installed:
  nodebox opengl library http://www.cityinabottle.org/nodebox/
  xdot command ("apt-get install xdot" in ubuntu or debian)

About
=====

Mepinta is a Python, C and C++ project.


